{"tid":430726,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"證監明年中推實名制 主席唐家成：毋須諮詢市場","createTime":"2017-10-10T05:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T17:06:24.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b362fefbe8610fcb356b4b0c5a1bd28803a6a1df","tid":430726,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T05:19:57.000Z","msg":"&lt;匯港通訊&gt; 證監會行政總裁歐達禮出席出席湯森路透泛亞監管峰時後表示，目標於明年中在互聯互通機制下推行實名制。被問到會否將實名制擴展至股票以外的其他金融產品，他稱則需要再觀察。<br />\n<br />\n在同一活動，歐達禮在演辭中指出，現時滬深港通佔本港成交量6%，料比例會持續增加，隨著跨境資金流加大，跨境式監管合作亦需要增加。他指，該會及中證監合作研究新機制作跨境監管。他指監察北向通投資的同時，將會要求南向通提供更大的透明度。(EC<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.quamnet.com/newscontent.action?listSectionCode=NEW_HOT&amp;articleId=5423421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.quamnet.com%2Fnewscontent.action%3FlistSectionCode%3DNEW_HOT%26articleId%3D5423421&d=6EIVBcTCt3Z5UoWiU1NYWZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=39b8ae36\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.quamnet.com/newscontent.action?listSectionCode=NEW_HOT&amp;articleId=5423421</a>"},{"pid":"e88292c89499e45d319f2dedb2479c2480bb08d8","tid":430726,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T05:20:36.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】「互聯互通」實施實名制計劃最快或於明年推行，證監會主席唐家成昨出席活動後首次明言，實名制不必修改上市規則，故此毋須向市場作諮詢，僅需要知會市場有關做法，讓市場有足夠時間作準備。<br />\n<br />\n券商難短期更換系統<br />\n他又稱，現時中證監、港交所（388）及證監會已致力商討實名制中，並冀望實名制可盡快推行，因制度對香港市場有正面作用，可與內地有更多交流，並對中港兩地市場維持良好質素。<br />\n現時內地A股已推行實名制，以便中證監即時追查市場操縱行為。公共專業聯盟財經政策發言人甄文星認為，雖然現時本港沒有設實名制，但證監基本上仍可透過多方面渠道追查來源，只是過程較漫長及繁複，認為本港落實實名制只是配合內地需要，但無可否認推實名制後可讓證監更快追查來源，「作用不大，只可以話係資訊快啲提供，不用下下出信去問。」<br />\n不過他認為，落實推行實名制後，券商需要更換結算系統及資料，「過程要好耐，亦要搵人手、搵資料」，因此認為短期內不會落實實名制，券商仍需時作準備。<br />\n另外，唐家成昨亦提到電視廣播（511，TVB）上周就回購計劃一事的司法覆核案，證監被法庭裁定敗訴一事。<br />\n他認為，法庭判電視廣播獲勝訴只是技術性問題，而法官亦指當中清洗豁免決定權，仍會由證監會收購及合併委員會決定，證監會繼續研究判詞，再決定下一步行動。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20171010/20178118\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20171010%2F20178118&d=6EIVBcTCt3Z5UoWiU1NYWZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=1a9ab4da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20171010%2F20178118&h=0c8f6a42\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20171010/20178118</a>"},{"pid":"486d1309d461e2d6459521a373425bb8b7845862","tid":430726,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T05:37:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n繼續唔好停"},{"pid":"dc9f57494da790f07866f03803cbe1ef0b9d30aa","tid":430726,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:04:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n繼續唔好停</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁嚴重竟然冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01b3158cc34d6a56267313a862fbda8478fa092","tid":430726,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a24478c485bbb436a47e8e10d11fad4e0caed61c","tid":430726,"uid":895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:34:08.000